<div class=3D"mw-heading mw-heading3"><h3 id=3D"First_properties">First pro=
perties</h3><span class=3D"mw-editsection"><span class=3D"mw-editsection-br=
acket">[</span><a href=3D"https://en.wikipedia.org/w/index.php?title=3DDete=
