perties"><span>edit</span></a><span class=3D"mw-editsection-bracket">]</spa=
n></span></div>
<p>The determinant has several key properties that can be proved by direct =
evaluation of the definition for <span class=3D"mwe-math-element mwe-math-e=
lement-inline"><span class=3D"mwe-math-mathml-inline mwe-math-mathml-a11y" =
style=3D"display: none;"><math xmlns=3D"http://www.w3.org/1998/Math/MathML"=
 alttext=3D"{\displaystyle 2\times 2}">
  <semantics>
