gin{pmatrix}1&amp;0\\0&amp;1\end{pmatrix}}}"></span> is 1.
Second, the determinant is zero if two rows are the same:
</p>
<dl><dd><span class=3D"mwe-math-element mwe-math-element-inline"><span clas=
