frac {n}{\operatorname {tr} \left(A^{-1}\right)}}\leq \det(A)^{\frac {1}{n}=
}\leq {\frac {1}{n}}\operatorname {tr} (A)\leq {\sqrt {{\frac {1}{n}}\opera=
