-image-inline mw-invert skin-invert" aria-hidden=3D"true" style=3D"vertical=
-align: -0.338ex; width:2.042ex; height:2.176ex;" alt=3D"{\displaystyle n!}=
"></span> (<span class=3D"mwe-math-element mwe-math-element-inline"><span c=
lass=3D"mwe-math-mathml-inline mwe-math-mathml-a11y" style=3D"display: none=
;"><math xmlns=3D"http://www.w3.org/1998/Math/MathML" alttext=3D"{\displays=
tyle n}">
